metadata.description: Seeds to Smoke is an artist designed series of Fine Art that captures the incredible process of creating Luxury Fine Cigars.  The artwork tells a unique story and honors all the workers in the cigar industry craft.  This one of a kind Fine Art NFT opportunity also offers a utility to Bo's Cigar Lounges. You won't want to miss this rare celebration collaboration of Fine Art and the Cigar Life Style available through the Ethereum Blockchain and the Metaverse.
